catpic - Download random cat images from TheCatAPI

Usage:
  catpic                       → Download 1 cat pic to default folder
  catpic /path/to/folder      → Download 1 cat pic to given folder
  catpic -number N [folder]   → Download N cat pics (max 1000) to folder
  catpic -df                  → Set default folder for downloads
  catpic -h                   → Show this help message
